channel.title: Java.exe eating all my cpu all of a sudden?! -.-
channel.description:
Okay, so i just added some item spawn points, compiled, and ran. Right after i ran, my client lagged like HELL. I closed runserver, and it stopped lagging. Before i added those 2 item spawns, when i ran it didnt lag at all. If i open taskmanager and then runserver, java.exe is using 96 - 99% of my CPU. -.-
[br][br][size=1]Posted on: July 15, 2008, 09:41:17 PM[/size][hr]Wow nvm, sorry for wasting forum space, turns out it was because i accidently deleted "spawnTimer=100;"
-.-
I dont know why that was cause java to lag like a bitch. :confused:
